{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-jsx","path":"/ghpage/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<blockquote>\n<p>github pages deploy하는 방법</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"packagejson에-하단에-있는-내용-추가하기-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#packagejson%EC%97%90-%ED%95%98%EB%8B%A8%EC%97%90-%EC%9E%88%EB%8A%94-%EB%82%B4%EC%9A%A9-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0-\" aria-label=\"packagejson에 하단에 있는 내용 추가하기  permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>package.json에 하단에 있는 내용 추가하기 !</h1>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">package.json</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"scripts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/* .... */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"deploy\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gh-pages -d build\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"predeploy\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"npm run build\"</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"homepage\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://[username].github.io/[github repository]\"</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>git remote -v 명령어를 입력하면 repository 명을 확인할 수 있음!</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>package.json에 내용 추가하고</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> run deploy</code></pre></div>\n<p>터미널에서 위 코드를 실행하고 5분 정도 기다리면 끝!</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">https://[username].github.io/[repository]</code> 들어가면 업데이트 되어있음 .</p>\n<hr>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Reference</strong></p>\n<p>nomade reactjs로 영화만들기 강의 참조</p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"title":"github pages Deploy","summary":"npm i gh-pages","date":"2023.01.10.","modifiedDate":null,"category":["git"],"tags":["git"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/95feaa556d35fbef637b04acfcb662af/3f3aa/react-image.png","srcSet":"/static/95feaa556d35fbef637b04acfcb662af/b66e8/react-image.png 134w,\n/static/95feaa556d35fbef637b04acfcb662af/da877/react-image.png 267w,\n/static/95feaa556d35fbef637b04acfcb662af/3f3aa/react-image.png 534w","sizes":"(min-width: 534px) 534px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/95feaa556d35fbef637b04acfcb662af/3f96d/react-image.webp 134w,\n/static/95feaa556d35fbef637b04acfcb662af/8a629/react-image.webp 267w,\n/static/95feaa556d35fbef637b04acfcb662af/c673b/react-image.webp 534w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 534px) 534px, 100vw"}]},"width":534,"height":113}},"publicURL":"/static/95feaa556d35fbef637b04acfcb662af/react-image.png"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/ghpage/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}